item.title: Fixing the TypeScript Error TS2792: Cannot Find Module '...'
item.description: Learn how to troubleshoot and fix the common TypeScript error ‘Cannot find module’ (example: undici-types), including modifying compiler options, adding path aliases, and reinstalling dependencies.
